WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:10.616
Hi, I just wanted to tell you another dream I had a while back that I want to get out there. I want to get this on the web to let people pray over this.

00:00:10.617 --> 00:00:22.138
I don't know if this is during the tribulation that this happens or if this happens before the tribulation, but you know, it's part of the birthing pains that happen.

00:00:22.139 --> 00:00:29.232
In this dream, there's a massive asteroid and it's coming into the Earth.

00:00:29.233 --> 00:00:40.566
I see it and everybody can see it, but you could hear it; it sounded like massive freight trains. Everything was shaking and moving so fast.

00:00:40.567 --> 00:00:48.358
I went outside in the dream and looked up, and it's just a massive streak of light, a fireball coming out of the sky.

00:00:48.359 --> 00:00:53.999
It was moving so quick and so fast that it sounded like the whole earth was shaking.

00:00:54.000 --> 00:01:07.003
It was incredible; this thing was humongous. In the dream, the United States tried to shoot it down with a laser beam.

00:01:07.004 --> 00:01:21.703
It was moving too quick to shoot it down with a rocket, so they used this laser beam that, in my dream, was green. They hit it with this laser weapon and it split the rock.

00:01:21.704 --> 00:01:33.546
This massive asteroid split in two and it busted up one half into little bitty fragments, but the other half was still massive.

00:01:33.547 --> 00:01:42.401
It hit by the islands, by San Juan, Puerto Rico, and the Bahamas—all that area out there.

00:01:42.402 --> 00:01:49.228
When it did, it crashed into the ocean and created this massive tsunami.

00:01:49.229 --> 00:02:01.936
I'm talking humongous, like 100 feet up or more. It was moving so quick and so fast; it covered the islands up.

00:02:01.937 --> 00:02:07.390
It covered Haiti; it covered those things up. It just went over the top of them.

00:02:07.391 --> 00:02:17.844
I could see it in the dream; these islands were just completely engulfed with water. It went clear into Africa.

00:02:17.845 --> 00:02:29.030
When it came into America, because it was so close, it hit Miami, North Carolina, and South Carolina—all that area.

00:02:29.031 --> 00:02:35.004
But the main area that I was shown in the dream was the Miami area and Fort Lauderdale.

00:02:35.005 --> 00:02:49.097
It went inland like the one that hit Japan; the tsunami wave washed in and just wiped out houses and buildings like they were nothing.

00:02:49.098 --> 00:02:59.486
It just blew them down. There were millions of people who were in trouble and lost. Many were dead, and the Lord had me praying.

00:02:59.487 --> 00:03:10.979
When I woke up the next day, He had me praying for these people that they would hear Him and that they would not be there at that time—that they would leave if this is something that was going to happen soon.

00:03:10.980 --> 00:03:17.863
I don't know, but I prayed for these people so they would get out of harm's way.

00:03:17.864 --> 00:03:25.364
It was just something that was very... when you wake up, you're in a cold sweat because it shook me.

00:03:25.365 --> 00:03:31.659
I was like, 'Lord, I have to tell people about this,'but I've just prayed over it.

00:03:31.660 --> 00:03:39.486
I could see that it was going to happen, and I don't know if we can stop it or prevent it or whatever.

00:03:39.487 --> 00:03:47.008
I just felt in my heart, this massive tsunami, this massive asteroid coming out of the sky.

00:03:47.009 --> 00:03:51.669
I've looked online at the NASA site to see, but they didn't know this was coming.

00:03:51.670 --> 00:03:57.148
They didn't announce it on TV; they didn't tell people that it was coming.

00:03:57.149 --> 00:04:10.550
It just happened and, like I said, it was humongous. It flew in and hit out there in the ocean, in the Atlantic. It caused devastation worldwide.

00:04:10.551 --> 00:04:20.765
I don't know if this is the Tribulation the Lord is showing me, or if it's something that happens in the birthing pains, but it's just one of the things I felt like I should share that the Lord has shown me.

00:04:20.766 --> 00:04:32.020
Thank you very much for watching. There are other things that the Lord showed me, and I'm going to tell those in other videos. Have a blessed day. Bye.

